             was indicted for <rs id="t18200112-75-off421" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200112-75-off421" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200112-75-off421" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200112-75-cd422" type="crimeDate">16th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200112-75-off421 t18200112-75-cd422"></join>, one whittle, value 5 s.; one piece of cotton, value 2 d., and one pocket-book, value 2 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200112-75-victim764" type="victimName">
                           Catharine 
                           Kealy
                        <interp inst="t18200112-75-victim764" type="surname" value="Kealy"></interp>
